<h1 class="font-bold uppercase text-center my-3">Panel De Administración</h1>
<div class="container flex justify-center items-center">

    <div class="menu-containers flex flex-column gap-2 align-normal lg:w-1/2">


        <div class="max-w-sm w-full lg:max-w-full lg:flex">
            <div class="h-48 lg:h-auto lg:w-48 flex-none bg-cover rounded-t lg:rounded-t-none lg:rounded-l text-center overflow-hidden" style="background-image: url('/icons/rol.jpeg')" title="Peticiones de Roles">
            </div>
            <div class="border-r border-b border-l border-gray-400 lg:border-l-0 lg:border-t lg:border-gray-400 bg-white rounded-b lg:rounded-b-none lg:rounded-r p-4 flex flex-col justify-between leading-normal">
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 flex items-center">
                        <svg class="fill-current text-gray-500 w-3 h-3 mr-2" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M4 8V6a6 6 0 1 1 12 0v2h1a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h1zm5 6.73V17h2v-2.27a2 2 0 1 0-2 0zM7 6v2h6V6a3 3 0 0 0-6 0z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Administrador
                    </p>
                    <div class="text-gray-900 font-bold text-xl mb-2">Peticiones de Roles</div>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 text-base">En esta pestaña podrás controlar las solicitudes de roles que hagan los diferentes usuarios del sistema en OnlyPan. Crea chefs, asigna moderadores o coordinadores, la elección es tuya.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="">
                    <a asp-action="ViewRolePetitions" asp-controller="Role" class="btn btn-primary">Ver Peticiones de roles</a>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="max-w-sm w-full lg:max-w-full lg:flex">
            <div class="h-48 lg:h-auto lg:w-48 flex-none bg-cover rounded-t lg:rounded-t-none lg:rounded-l text-center overflow-hidden" style="background-image: url('/icons/commentary.jpg')" title="Comentarios Reportados">
            </div>
            <div class="border-r border-b border-l border-gray-400 lg:border-l-0 lg:border-t lg:border-gray-400 bg-white rounded-b lg:rounded-b-none lg:rounded-r p-4 flex flex-col justify-between leading-normal">
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 flex items-center">
                        <svg class="fill-current text-gray-500 w-3 h-3 mr-2" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M4 8V6a6 6 0 1 1 12 0v2h1a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h1zm5 6.73V17h2v-2.27a2 2 0 1 0-2 0zM7 6v2h6V6a3 3 0 0 0-6 0z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Administrador
                    </p>
                    <div class="text-gray-900 font-bold text-xl mb-2">Comentarios Reportados</div>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 text-base">En esta pestaña podrás regular los comentarios que hayan sido reportados por la comunidad. Elige si eliminarlos del foro correspondiente o dejarlos allí.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="item">
                    <a asp-action="Comments" asp-controller="Admin" class="btn btn-primary">Ver comentarios reportados</a>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-sm w-full lg:max-w-full lg:flex">
            <div class="h-48 lg:h-auto lg:w-48 flex-none bg-cover rounded-t lg:rounded-t-none lg:rounded-l text-center overflow-hidden" style="background-image: url('/icons/commentary.jpg')" title="Comentarios Reportados">
            </div>
            <div class="border-r border-b border-l border-gray-400 lg:border-l-0 lg:border-t lg:border-gray-400 bg-white rounded-b lg:rounded-b-none lg:rounded-r p-4 flex flex-col justify-between leading-normal">
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 flex items-center">
                        <svg class="fill-current text-gray-500 w-3 h-3 mr-2" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M4 8V6a6 6 0 1 1 12 0v2h1a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h1zm5 6.73V17h2v-2.27a2 2 0 1 0-2 0zM7 6v2h6V6a3 3 0 0 0-6 0z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Administrador
                    </p>
                    <div class="text-gray-900 font-bold text-xl mb-2">Donaciones Hechas</div>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 text-base">En esta pestaña podrás regular los comentarios que hayan sido reportados por la comunidad. Elige si eliminarlos del foro correspondiente o dejarlos allí.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="item">
                    <a asp-action="Donations" asp-controller="Admin" class="btn btn-primary">Ver Donaciónes Realizadas</a>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>